    "name": "Amikin Village",
    "steam_appid": 3104430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Amikin Village》将激烈的生存游戏玩法与收集神奇生物的刺激感融合在一起。在这里，Amikins——可爱而又凶猛的生物——是你成功的关键，帮助你从战斗到制作的每一个环节。捕捉并进化多样的Amikins，管理资源，建造你的魔法基地，并在一个提供无尽冒险和挑战的世界中生存下来。这是带有乐趣的生存——完美适合每个人中的英雄！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104430/extras/ba904c4f8e3278888ba8d0bae75bfdd3.avif?t=1746599665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104430/extras_big/ba904c4f8e3278888ba8d0bae75bfdd3.avif?t=1746599665 width=800 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 <strong>Amikin盟友：收集它们所有！</strong> 🌟</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险进入荒野，发现Amikins，这些拥有无与伦比力量和奇特个性的神秘生物。这些忠诚的伙伴是你生存和成功的关键。当你聚集你独特的团队时，为了融合乐趣、策略和意想不到的友谊，这些友谊为你的探索增添活力，做好准备吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104430/extras/3bd946b0ff1458b2c643137cf04002c6.avif?t=1746599665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104430/extras_big/3bd946b0ff1458b2c643137cf04002c6.avif?t=1746599665 width=800 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏠 <strong>家园基地：用魔法自动化！</strong> 🏠</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将你的基地从一个简单的避难所转变为Amikins带领下的魔法总部。他们独特的能力使得管理你的避风港变得轻而易举，自动化任务并为你的日常磨砺增添一丝魔法。看着你的基地变成一个繁忙的活动和魔法的中心，这都要归功于你的Amikin朋友们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104430/extras/94e781d0d968d9bcf4480123df13a8b8.avif?t=1746599665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104430/extras_big/94e781d0d968d9bcf4480123df13a8b8.avif?t=1746599665 width=800 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧬 <strong>力量游行：合并与培育！</strong> 🧬</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过合并相同种类来释放你的Amikins的全部潜力，使它们的力量得到增强，并培育它们继承最优秀的特质。这种战略性的力量游戏确保你的团队随时准备应对任何事情，使每个Amikin都成为其本身的冠军。这是一个有趣、有回报的过程，让你的队伍更接近于不可战胜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104430/extras/60c02a7098399946bb85734d9c057d50.avif?t=1746599665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104430/extras_big/60c02a7098399946bb85734d9c057d50.avif?t=1746599665 width=800 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚀 <strong>史诗探索：奇幻遇见科幻！</strong> 🚀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上一场穿越“Amikin Village”广阔世界的宏大旅程，这个世界充满了秘密和奇幻与科幻元素的混合。你从另一个领域的到来为这片神秘的土地带来了独特的技术和魔法混合。装备着未来科技和你的Amikins的魔法，探索古老的废墟、密集的森林以及介于两者之间的一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104430/extras/93011c368435864822133d8757a06766.avif?t=1746599665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104430/extras_big/93011c368435864822133d8757a06766.avif?t=1746599665 width=800 height=133 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😺 <strong>梗图魔法：笑声保证！</strong> 😺 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入一个可爱、魔法和梗图相撞的游戏！“Amikin Village”以那些喜欢保持事物轻松有趣的可爱Amikins将幽默带到前沿。参与异想天开的冒险，并通过流行文化的点头表示，确保你的旅程充满了欢乐和笑声。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104430/extras/ed8eaa92b8099f8d328aefc03a9d62ca.avif?t=1746599665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104430/extras_big/ed8eaa92b8099f8d328aefc03a9d62ca.avif?t=1746599665 width=800 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>准备好进行一次难忘的冒险了吗？</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Amikin Village”在等着你，将生存、策略和纯粹的乐趣融合在一个魔法世界中。建立你的基地，培养你的Amikin团队，并探索一个每天都是新冒险的广阔领域。立即下载并开始你充满魔法、挑战和伙伴关系的史诗之旅。你在“Amikin Village”世界的故事今天就开始！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104430/extras/d661de1ad6648d91ceb2b4a26c0936bf.avif?t=1746599665\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104430/extras_big/d661de1ad6648d91ceb2b4a26c0936bf.avif?t=1746599665 width=800 height=132 /></span></p>",
